PrecisAppointment of MARYANNE KINGMA of Calgary, Alberta, to be a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and designation of MARYANNE KINGMA to be Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (Vancouver Regional Office); effective August 4, 2015.
